<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 20px; line-height: 1.6; }
        .warning { color: red; font-weight: bold; }
        .output { border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 10px; margin-top: 15px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1><%= title %></h1>
    <p class="warning">
        WARNING: This page is intentionally vulnerable to Reflected XSS. Do not deploy publicly.
    </p>

    <p>The query parameter 'q' is rendered directly without sanitization.</p>

    <div class="output">
        You searched for:
        <!-- WARNING: Intentionally vulnerable code. Input is rendered directly. -->
        <%- input %>
    </div>

    <p>Try appending <code>?q=&lt;script&gt;alert('XSS')&lt;/script&gt;</code> to the URL.</p>

    <p><a href="/">Back to Home</a></p>
</body>
</html>
